  <header>
    <h1>Solai Dam Tragedy</h1>
    <p>A tragic event that exposed regulatory and environmental failures.</p>
  </header>
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
      <li><a href="#charges">Nature of Charges</a></li>
